Module GetCapabilities¶

This module parses OGC Web Processing Service (WPS) GetCapabilities request.

Class Post¶

class pywps.Parser.GetCapabilities.Post(wps)¶

Parses input request obtained via HTTP POST encoding - should be XML file.

parse(document, initInputs=None)¶

Parse the requested XML document

Class Get¶

class pywps.Parser.GetCapabilities.Get(wps)¶

Parses input request obtained via HTTP GET encoding.

parse(unparsedInputs, initInputs=None)¶

Parse rawly parsed inputs
